{"tid":1723493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論] 星期六日：和你Bike 暨 黃店爆買日","createTime":"2019-11-15T08:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T11:00:23.000Z","uid":189283,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c034c2fb7613e789919159fb2a90c00b770a45cf","tid":1723493,"uid":189283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:05:33.000Z","msg":"追過post見到<br />\n星期一至五朝早做嘢，星期六日休息係大多數共識<br />\n<br />\n我提出星期六日搞個<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「和你Bike 暨 黃店爆買日」</span></span></strong><br />\n一來大家都知本土店LocoBike幾好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二來依幾日黃店肯陪我哋罷市，佢哋冇收入淨交租係幾甘<br />\n趁星期六日推動黃色經濟圈好唔好？<br />\n大家一齊勁踩LocoBike，勁買黃店<br />\n藍店就算開門都係拍烏蠅，蝕死佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n風險仲低過和你Shop，和理非可以全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>求認真討論<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反對</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd92ff0b5feed301cee80cd9928824cde3f612a","tid":1723493,"uid":189283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:06:25.000Z","msg":"自推，認真討論 1/20"},{"pid":"8d87ce78719514d319ec3e50541710d46e085b52","tid":1723493,"uid":189283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:06:51.000Z","msg":"自推，認真討論 2/20"},{"pid":"2cc5efde60b7e9bb2ff5846587e4254baefa692b","tid":1723493,"uid":189283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:07:08.000Z","msg":"自推，認真討論 3/20"},{"pid":"c54ee2f421e7afc1e94211a7ffc058c156bc916e","tid":1723493,"uid":189283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:07:37.000Z","msg":"自推，認真討論 4/20"},{"pid":"3c09416fe677801a32d55ac13ab68379ffadfc33","tid":1723493,"uid":189283,"like":0,"d